00:03:22.230 --> 00:03:25.630
When we think TV, we're
thinking video-based

00:03:25.630 --> 00:03:27.930
performance, we're thinking
graphic-based performance

00:03:27.930 --> 00:03:28.560
that's out there.

00:03:28.560 --> 00:03:31.860
So where it complements, I
think, is on that L9 chipset.

00:03:31.860 --> 00:03:35.370
When I look at things like
Novellus developing, or even

00:03:35.370 --> 00:03:37.590
