important just for those fast

00:03:41.730 --> 00:03:47.620
transitions or for faster
applications across the board.

00:03:47.620 --> 00:03:51.280
We're looking forward to opening
up the capabilities of

00:03:51.280 --> 00:03:53.820
what the software side can do.

00:03:53.820 --> 00:03:56.800
