TV actually looks smaller.

00:08:54.890 --> 00:09:01.420
And so the information density
is not as great.

00:09:01.420 --> 00:09:05.120
So you need to think about TVs
differently than you do a

00:09:05.120 --> 00:09:10.830
computer or a tablet, and not
put as much information.

00:09:10.830 --> 00:09:12.920
Put bigger things up there.

00:09:12.920 --> 00:09:19.082
Make it more fun but more
focused in a sense.

00:09:19.082 --> 00:09:24.550
