00:09:34.910 --> 00:09:38.170
This is about a bunch of
people sitting down and

00:09:38.170 --> 00:09:40.750
watching something or
using something.

00:09:40.750 --> 00:09:43.800
So the apps that really take
advantage of that-- and you

00:09:43.800 --> 00:09:47.100
can speak to this-- are the
ones that are really gonna

00:09:47.100 --> 00:09:50.630
take advantage of that
social experience.

00:09:50.630 --> 00:09:51.478
LES VOGEL: Yeah.

00:09:51.478 --> 00:09:52.750
ALAN QUEEN: Yeah, definitely.

00:09:52.750 --> 00:09:55.020
I think that when we
use our mobile

00:09:55.020 --> 00:09:56.200
devices, that's a very--

00:09:56.200 --> 00:09:57.720
like you said, it's a
personal experience.

00:09:57.720 --> 00:09:59.670
