common to everyone in the

00:10:02.160 --> 00:10:04.320
house most of the time, you
know, when you have it above

00:10:04.320 --> 00:10:05.570
your fireplace or things
like that.

00:10:05.570 --> 00:10:08.120
So it's a very social
experience, where everyone's

00:10:08.120 --> 00:10:09.140
in the living room
watching it.

00:10:09.140 --> 00:10:12.000
So being able to take advantage
of not just a larger

00:10:12.000 --> 00:10:16.000
screen, but that social nature
is what we're all about.

00:10:16.000 --> 00:10:19.120
Creating multi-screen
applications for multiple

00:10:19.120 --> 00:10:21.450
