Everyone's already in their
living room using these

00:10:29.610 --> 00:10:32.630
devices while they watch TV,
so we're trying to take

00:10:32.630 --> 00:10:34.930
advantage of that, and let
people actually be social

00:10:34.930 --> 00:10:38.610
around the TV, rather than just
looking at their phone

00:10:38.610 --> 00:10:40.620
while they're watching TV
and ignoring each other.

00:10:40.620 --> 00:10:42.580
So anyway, that's just another
aspect that we think is really

00:10:42.580 --> 00:10:45.280
great about bringing
applications to the TV.

