living room, we want to make

00:14:01.170 --> 00:14:03.830
sure that they feel comfortable
as soon as they go

00:14:03.830 --> 00:14:05.974
into that app.

00:14:05.974 --> 00:14:10.000
And I love that I feel like
we've been able to make

00:14:10.000 --> 00:14:17.310
something that draws you in
instead of making you feel

00:14:17.310 --> 00:14:21.644
overwhelmed by information
on your screen.

00:14:21.644 --> 00:14:23.830
ALAN QUEEN: I don't want
to turn this into a UX

00:14:23.830 --> 00:14:26.095
discussion, but it brought up
an interesting thing that I

00:14:26.095 --> 00:14:29.120
