your finding all

00:15:13.455 --> 00:15:16.620
your content, and using the TV
to really act as the anchor

00:15:16.620 --> 00:15:20.660
point in the display area
for the device.

00:15:20.660 --> 00:15:22.590
And obviously for Google
TV, we're able to

00:15:22.590 --> 00:15:23.420
do that very easily.

00:15:23.420 --> 00:15:25.650
So we've been really happy
with the experience.

