00:19:18.770 --> 00:19:20.330
DJs and hosts.

00:19:20.330 --> 00:19:23.470
And so we want to really try
to tie that in and make it

00:19:23.470 --> 00:19:26.920
feel even more social when it's
in people's living rooms.

